{
  "stem": "268.9",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like chopped beef-- army food-- and oranges and apples and bananas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh, gosh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived on oranges and apples.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't see oranges and apples in years, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I lived on that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And unfortunately, bad weather came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to get rid of it go over the banister into the ocean.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the food was great.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they treated us well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had shows on board.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had my little harmonica with me, and I played that too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were so happy, not a penny-- didn't have anything, didn't know the language, but happy to come to-- to-- to a country which-- and I must say, I can't say enough about the hospitality and the greatness of this country.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They welcomed us with open arms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "GIs returning after the war, looking for jobs, and here we are, looking for jobs also and for places to live.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow, we didn't hear the anti-Semitic slogans that we heard when we left Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were in the home of the free, finally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I know we've talked a lot, but how we can one-- what comes to mind is sad, acts of-- acts of-- inhumane acts of murderous acts, and some humane acts too.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I witnessed someone having his head split open to acts of courage, like helping the stragglers at the end who couldn't march anymore on the death march.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one or two guys would carry him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I didn't want to come to that point.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's why I wanted to make a run for it, unless-- death march-- someone should carry me, because as you carried and helped the straggling, the dying one, like on the ocean, they would pull you down with you.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
